&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Blogger for podcasting&amp;rdquo; is an open opportunity for somebody out there to provide a lot of value (and make a lot of money doing it).&amp;#160;&lt;a href=&#34;#fnref:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-backref&#34; role=&#34;doc-backlink&#34;&gt;&amp;#x21a9;&amp;#xfe0e;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
