&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://detoursapp.com&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/dock.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;dock&#34; width=&#34;380&#34; height=&#34;218&#34; class=&#34;aligncenter size-full wp-image-941&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
